<br />
<br />I know, but this is definitely a challenge we'll have to face for this setup. That's why I've started on the test ROM so early <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /> The good news is Nintendulator is not used for playing ROMs (for fun anyway <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />), and it has a modular mapper interface. I am looking into providing both a revised MMC5 mapper that would support CHR-RAM and an NESDEV1-specific mapper that would emulate the actual hardware mapper (for compliance testing of software).</div>

